            <fr:title text="Forester 3.0 › breaking changes"><fr:link href="foreign-forester-jms-00CW.xml" title="Forester 3.0" addr="//forester/jms-00CW" type="local">Forester 3.0</fr:link> › breaking changes</fr:title>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p><fr:link href="foreign-forester-jms-00CW.xml" title="Forester 3.0" addr="//forester/jms-00CW" type="local">Forester 3.0</fr:link> introduces a number of breaking changes to the source language in order to facilitate maintainability, diagnostic support, and extensibility of both the Forester tool and your individual <fr:link href="foreign-forester-tfmt-000R.xml" title="Forests and trees of evergreen notes" addr="//forester/tfmt-000R" type="local">forests</fr:link>.</fr:p>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
