          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>As a consequence of the <fr:link href="foreign-forester-jms-00CZ.xml" title="Forester 3.0 › breaking changes › fall-through of undefined identifiers" addr="//forester/jms-00CZ" type="local">changed fallthrough behavior</fr:link>, several new primitives have been added to the source language, including <fr:code><![CDATA[\p]]></fr:code>, <fr:code><![CDATA[\em]]></fr:code>, <fr:code><![CDATA[\strong]]></fr:code>, <fr:code><![CDATA[\ol]]></fr:code>, <fr:code><![CDATA[\ul]]></fr:code>, <fr:code><![CDATA[\li]]></fr:code>, <fr:code><![CDATA[\blockquote]]></fr:code>, and <fr:code><![CDATA[\pre]]></fr:code>.</fr:p>
            <fr:p>You can add further commands to your primitives using a combination of <fr:code><![CDATA[\def]]></fr:code>, <fr:code><![CDATA[\iftex]]></fr:code>, and <fr:code><![CDATA[\xml]]></fr:code>.</fr:p>
