                <fr:taxon>Feature</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <fr:p><fr:link href="foreign-forester-jms-00CW.xml" title="Forester 3.0" addr="//forester/jms-00CW" type="local">Forester 3.0</fr:link> adds proper diagnostics and error messages, via the excellent <fr:link href="https://ocaml.org/p/asai/latest" type="external">asai</fr:link> library maintained by <fr:link href="foreign-forester-favonia.xml" title="Kuen-Bang Hou (Favonia)" addr="//forester/favonia" type="local">Favonia</fr:link>. When something goes wrong in your forest, the terminal output should expain what happened while displaying the precise location in your source file.</fr:p>
