                <fr:title text="Lightweight templating in forester new">Lightweight templating in <fr:code>forester new</fr:code></fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Feature</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <fr:p><fr:link href="foreign-forester-jms-00CW.xml" title="Forester 3.0" addr="//forester/jms-00CW" type="local">Forester 3.0</fr:link> adds a new <fr:code>--template</fr:code> option to the <fr:code>forester new</fr:code> command. Running <fr:code>forester new --template xxx-0001</fr:code> will create a new tree with the contents of the existing tree <fr:code>xxx-0001</fr:code>.</fr:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
