              <fr:mainmatter>
                <fr:p>A new <fr:code>--assets-dirs</fr:code> option has been added to the <fr:code>forester build</fr:code> command, which can be used to supply multiple directories containing static assets that should be copied into the forest. By default, the option is set to <fr:code>assets</fr:code>.</fr:p>
